description:
This is a 11 minute workout called '10-minute ENCORE | Add to ANY workout!' from the channel Kaleigh Cohen Cycling.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Add this 10-minute encore to the end of any cycling workout to take your training to the next level!! This quick 10-minute challenge is packed with motivating songs and challenging pushes!! I am so excited you decided to take this extra challenge!!
